  <summary date="2020-04-03T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Hazard Pay Expansion Act

This bill permits the uniformed services to pay hazardous duty pay to a servicemember who, during a declared national public health emergency, performs duty deemed hazardous based upon frequent exposure to the cause of that public health emergency.</summary>
